review_text:
I joined the gym back in August 2024 when it first opened, primarily because of its promixity to where I live and the convenience of being able to go to the gym any time of the day.

My most favourite memories of AF BBC are:
• going to the gym during the wee hours of the weekends, so that I can be home before the rest of my family wakes up - nothing like a peaceful gym workout to start the day;
• the quality and range of gym equipment - yes, this is far smaller than a lot of commercial gyms out there, but it is definitely sufficient for a good workout;
• seeing familiar faces of Bukit Batok neighbours and plucking up the courage to make friends and connections.

10/10 would recommend AF BBC to anyone looking to start their fitness journey! The good thing about the gym being small is that it feels less daunting than the bigger gyms out there, and most of the gym-goers are regular folks like you and me who are taking an active step to a healthy lifestyle. Give it a try!
